      "content": "Please stop worrying about what you think it is; sharp pain moving to the lower right side is a sign that you need to be seen by a medical professional immediately. Do not mix ibuprofen and codeine without a doctor's explicit instruction, as this can be dangerous. For your immediate comfort, try a heating pad on the area while you arrange to get checked out.",
